@@TJvRunOption
Description:
This is the set of options used in the TJvRunDlg. 

* roNoBrowse : if this option is checked, the browse button is not visible. 
* roNoDefault : if this option is checked, there is no default Value. if not, the default Value is the last one used. 
* roCalcDirectory : if this option is checked, the dialog calculates the working directory from the file name. 
* roNoLabel : if this option is checked, the label on the left side of the combobox will be hided. 
* roNoSeparateMem : if this option is checked, it will removes the separate memory space check box (Windows NT only).

